Registry
2014", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC7370.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document recommends some editorial changes to the IANA IS-IS TLV Codepoints registry to more accurately document the state of the protocol.  It also sets out new guidelines for Designated Experts to apply when reviewing allocations from the registry."];
